Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.54,0:00:17.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什麼時候在圍牆上作了這種手腳？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.22,0:00:20.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}很早以前就準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.36,0:00:22.03,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為了能隨時逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.49,0:00:26.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}虧你還是我的護衛  真是盡職盡責啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:29.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒時間說風涼話了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.63,0:00:30.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.18,0:00:34.99,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}見到母親大人之前  不管是什麼樣的辛酸我都會忍住的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.47,0:00:39.22,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這一段路面很糟  小心點腳下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.70,0:00:42.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就這點小事而已  輕而易…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:43.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我才剛說完…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.79,0:00:46.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈大人  您沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:49.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}裏葉你看我這樣還叫沒事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:51.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}太暗了  看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.13,0:00:54.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}希望外邊的衣服別弄髒了才好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.72,0:00:56.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}比起主人來你更關心衣服嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.03,0:00:59.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈和裏葉都把衣服掀起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.21,0:01:04.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哎？ 兩個人一起做嗎？ 柳也大人也太壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.33,0:01:06.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真是的  跟禽獸一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.22,0:01:09.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你們聽懂我在說什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.83,0:01:12.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我讓你們把衣服捲起來  這樣便於行路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.02,0:01:14.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}追兵應該已經逼近了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.87,0:01:15.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.04,0:02:55.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別離開我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:18.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}快跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.44,0:03:25.96,AIR Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,770)}山    路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:42.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可以動彈了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:46.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.09,0:03:49.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}難為你能不叫出聲來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:03:53.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別小看我  我可不是那種膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:55.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}快點動身吧  不然就扔下你一個人走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.85,0:03:57.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那邊是我們來的方向呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.83,0:04:04.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看來追兵還真不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.48,0:04:07.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}裏葉  你帶著神奈的衣服了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:14.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你們倆就坐在那邊歇著好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.43,0:04:16.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不要離開這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.18,0:04:16.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:17.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:25.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在那邊！ 是個女的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:27.51,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}跑得還真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:29.19,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別盯丟了！ 快追！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.08,0:04:42.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}女的掉進河裏了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.12,0:04:44.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好像掉進河裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:46.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}聽起來好像就在這下邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:47.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看！ 是衣服！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:50.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}把大家都叫過來  快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:53.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在下流！ 好好地搜索河的下流！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:02.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}把刀扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:08.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}老實回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.02,0:05:10.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}老實一點的話我就饒你一條命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:13.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你們是從關東來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:15.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為什麼要追殺神奈備命？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.72,0:05:18.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不知道  只是這樣被命令的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:20.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你們打算把神奈備命怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:22.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是誰下的命令？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:25.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不知道  我們只是在服從頭領的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:26.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.25,0:05:31.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:41.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你打算殺了他嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:44.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不這樣做的話  我們的生命就有危險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:46.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你不覺得羞恥嗎  白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.83,0:05:51.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你剛才不是說過要饒他一命嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:53.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你就這麼輕易地撒謊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.31,0:05:56.42,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你就這麼輕易地違背誓言嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:59.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這要看時間和場合了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.89,0:06:03.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你是說  向我許下的誓言  也會因時間和場合而違背嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:09.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你就這麼輕易地殺害別人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:12.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.71,0:06:15.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我不想被這樣的人保護
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:19.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我命令你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:24.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}只要你還當我是主人  今後就不允許再殺生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.83,0:06:25.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}給我記住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:31.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:33.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}明白就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:36.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.44,0:06:40.85,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一個人也不殺的話  你以為我們還能逃掉嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:43.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}只要有柳也大人在  我想一定輕而易舉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:46.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別說得這麼簡單啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:53.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可以放鬆點了  附近沒有追兵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:55.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:58.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}裏葉  不好意思  能取點水來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:00.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}下邊應該有河的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.95,0:07:02.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.83,0:07:07.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:11.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別跟我說話  頭好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.23,0:07:14.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是中暑了吧  來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.75,0:07:17.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:19.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}給身體降降溫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.05,0:07:23.03,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你倒是先打個招呼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.43,0:07:24.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那好  我要倒水了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:29.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我是說你就不能再溫柔些了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:31.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別那麼囉嗦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.87,0:07:35.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你這白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.59,0:07:37.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:39.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈大人  已經這麼精神了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:41.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:43.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小孩子恢復得就是快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.39,0:07:45.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我才不是精神了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.72,0:07:47.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是發怒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:51.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可是  真愁人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:54.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}夏天要越來越熱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:58.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}穿著這身衣服到處走的話  很快就會中暑的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:07:59.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:02.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我已經準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.57,0:08:05.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}來吧  神奈大人  到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:08.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:13.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哎呀哎呀  再這麼不聽話  我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:20.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哎呀哎呀  身上已經出了這麼多汗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:23.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂！ 別摸那裏啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:25.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  果然是呢  連裏邊都濕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:27.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}快住手  很癢的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:32.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不是說過快住手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.83,0:08:36.51,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:39.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈大人的衣服被那只猿猴給…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:41.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}快還給我  不要臉的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.36,0:08:44.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}閃開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:48.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真漂亮  柳也大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:51.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  這才是我的忠臣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.42,0:08:58.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}傻… 傻瓜！ 快停手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.42,0:08:59.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不  我不停手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.75,0:09:03.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}居然趁著主人換衣服時闖進來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:05.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}大逆不道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.58,0:09:08.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你不是剛剛才說我是忠臣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.37,0:09:10.50,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別找那種不講理的借口了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.81,0:09:12.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}主人才是不講理呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.87,0:09:15.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:20.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這衣服到底是從哪裏找來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:24.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看到河邊曬著洗完的衣服  我就借來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.72,0:09:26.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}當然  留下了衣服錢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:29.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}很合身嘛  神奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:30.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是… 是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.57,0:09:33.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你的興趣還真怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:35.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼看都是個很棒的鄉村女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.17,0:09:38.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}都有些可愛過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:40.19,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就是有點壯實而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.94,0:09:42.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:56.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一點起色也沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:09:59.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}學東西都是開頭時最關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.27,0:10:04.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}只要學會了基礎  很快就會熟練起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:08.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}要用這個練習嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.41,0:10:12.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}手包本來就是用石頭做的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.33,0:10:15.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}打到自己會很疼的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.15,0:10:19.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就是要有一些風險  人才會更認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:22.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我說… 手包可不是這麼危險的遊戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:23.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}開始吧  神奈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:25.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}居然不理我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.47,0:10:35.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.64,0:10:36.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  還好吧  神奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:39.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:48.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}睡得很香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:52.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}活動一下才會睡得更香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.09,0:10:56.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}過去一直都被關在社殿裏了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:10:58.85,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:02.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}裏葉也休息一下吧  明天還要走山路的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:05.19,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也大人不是也累了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:07.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我沒事的  這種事都習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:09.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是戰爭嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:10.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:19.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}請您還是多少休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:21.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我會替您望風的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:28.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:09.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我這裏有好貨哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.22,0:12:16.42,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看起來是個很大的集市呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:18.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}集市是什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:20.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是買賣商品的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.29,0:12:25.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可別大聲嚷啊  我們都是被通緝的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:28.85,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我知道  我也沒傻到那個地步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.33,0:12:31.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}裏葉  這是什麼東西啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.36,0:12:36.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這叫做烏梅  是治療腹痛的藥物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:39.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就是那個酸死人的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:41.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哦  還有年糕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:45.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}從前  神奈大人因為一口氣吃得太多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.65,0:12:48.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}塞在喉嚨裏了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.65,0:12:51.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為太好吃  實在忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.49,0:12:53.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:55.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}大概是白酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.09,0:12:58.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}從前  神奈大人因為喝得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.14,0:13:01.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}瘋鬧了好一陣  最後…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:04.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別總提這種無聊的舊事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:08.42,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我說啊  忘了我剛才說過別大聲嚷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:10.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:15.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}既然這麼熱鬧  多少說笑一些也不會顯眼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.41,0:13:19.22,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}況且  在這人山人海裏誰又能看出我來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:22.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}反正很壯實的  怎麼看都是鄉村女孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.05,0:13:25.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}還在記著那無聊的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:27.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}知道了  算我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:30.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你很可愛  可愛得都壯絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:33.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你引人注目得不得了  所以還是給我老實一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:38.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你的誇獎裏總是一點誠意也沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.44,0:13:42.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這位大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.51,0:13:45.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這個長著花紋的球是什麼東西啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:46.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是瓜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.95,0:13:50.99,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}瓜不是那種更軟更有水分的東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:53.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這麼硬的話會咬不動的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:56.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你是哪裏的大小姐啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:13:58.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}從這裏步行十天左右的山裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.32,0:14:04.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別在意  這丫頭多少有些癡呆  真傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.28,0:14:06.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那可真難為你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:12.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你說誰癡呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.09,0:14:15.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}除了你還能有誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:17.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}裏葉也說點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.78,0:14:19.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.47,0:14:20.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}裏葉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:23.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你在哪啊  裏葉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.50,0:14:27.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}疼疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.56,0:14:28.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別咬啊別咬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:31.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}還不是因為你自己太粗魯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.82,0:14:35.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}整整半天都用來照看神奈了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:38.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}裏葉究竟到哪裏去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:44.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我還從來沒見過像你這麼醜的鳥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:48.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}叫聲這麼難聽  也難怪沒人會買了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:52.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}杜鵑和三寶鳥的叫聲都要更好聽些的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.71,0:14:55.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}疼疼疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:05.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一隻鳥居然也敢嘲笑我  太無禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:10.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看我不把你那可笑的尾巴連根拔光才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:28.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}拜託你快停下吧  它可是我最上等的一隻長尾雞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:32.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}接下來要去看什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:35.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}得先去找到裏葉才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.27,0:15:37.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}武士大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.70,0:15:43.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}武士大人  還請您施捨一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:49.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我三天前被人從村裏趕了出來  兩手空空地逃到了這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:50.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是戰亂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.45,0:15:52.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.50,0:15:56.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}只是一群粗暴的武士們命令我們離開的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.95,0:15:59.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}屋舍和田地全都被沒收了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.12,0:16:01.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那可真是苦了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:09.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這位姑娘  莫非是哪裏的貴人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.63,0:16:11.50,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哦  你看得出來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:17.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不  絕對沒有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:22.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我是個普普通通的可愛的田舍女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:24.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}只是多少有些壯實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:26.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}還在為這個慪氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:31.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你還發什麼呆啊  快施捨他點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:33.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可施捨什麼才好啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:38.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也不是什麼貴重東西  不過還是能換點錢應急吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:43.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}多謝您了  這個大恩我莫齒難忘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:45.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}要好好活下去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:52.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}做了件好事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:54.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這也未必呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:56.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:58.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就是說  可能都是在騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:02.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我若餓得不行了的話  也會去騙人奉承人的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.69,0:17:06.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這些遭遇之類的話  真相信才是傻瓜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:09.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你果然很傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:13.19,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}他那一身皮包骨頭可不是裝出來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:16.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是嗎？ 原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.05,0:17:23.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過  肚子餓了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:26.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}剛對你另眼看待了  你就這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.33,0:17:29.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為神奈大人還在發育期嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:35.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}要發育的話就別長在屁股上  要是胸部再豐滿一些的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:36.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:39.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你好像沒精神啊  裏葉  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:41.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你們都不吃驚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.15,0:17:44.26,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇  裏葉  你是什麼時候回來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:45.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我一點也沒注意到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.18,0:17:48.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}裏葉可真是神出鬼沒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.41,0:17:53.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}感謝你們毫無誠意的關心了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.06,0:17:55.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你到底去哪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:58.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這件事待會再說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.42,0:18:01.42,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}對了  我給神奈大人帶回了件禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:05.71,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是胡桃嗎  這個季節裏還真少見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:09.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神社附近有一顆早熟的枝條  據說是幸運物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:13.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}又是神奈大人喜歡吃的東西  而且還有營養
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:17.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真是的  你不在的時候可真苦了我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.19,0:18:21.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哎呀哎呀  神奈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:23.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別追了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.71,0:18:29.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}裏葉  你該不是把神奈推給我逃掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:33.99,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也只有柳也大人才會有如此不敬的想法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:44.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為什麼打不開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.52,0:18:46.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}算了算了  會把牙崩掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.53,0:18:47.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}讓我也做點什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:52.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}總讓你們幹活的話  我會過意不去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:18:56.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那就去撿點乾柴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:58.96,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}另外  把胡桃放下吧  我給你打開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:00.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:03.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那我就去撿柴了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.29,0:19:04.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.56,0:19:07.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別跑得太遠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:09.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.14,0:19:16.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}剛才那個集市的前邊  設立了一個關卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:20.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}專門挑選年輕的女孩  檢查她們的後背
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.64,0:19:22.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}大概是想檢查背後的羽翼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.46,0:19:26.50,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那我們就不能再在街道上走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:29.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可你居然也能注意到這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:33.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在那裏開集市的話  有些不太方便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.78,0:19:37.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我感到有些奇怪  所以檢查了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:39.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你可真是精通世事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:40.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}多虧你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:46.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這麼高明的武藝  是在哪裏學來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.22,0:19:48.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這只不過是雜耍罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.26,0:19:52.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過  也不能讓手變生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:54.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可別跟神奈說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:57.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}要是她說什麼胡桃也是生命的話可就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:20:01.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}「今後不允許再殺生」嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.49,0:20:05.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你以為我真的會遵守這個諾言嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:11.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}其實神奈大人一直不讓我說出口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:15.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你還記得逃出捨殿那個晚上的事情吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.12,0:20:22.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那之後  神奈大人聽到了追兵的哨聲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.50,0:20:26.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也正在被人追趕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:31.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}必須快點去  我不去的話柳也就會被殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.09,0:20:36.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}如果柳也死了的話  我… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:41.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}即使我告訴她這是策略  她也聽不進去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.87,0:20:44.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:49.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}恕我多言  我想柳也大人一定會遵守不殺的諾言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:51.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:55.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}假如那個時候  神奈大人命令你殺了那個人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:20:58.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也大人又會怎樣做？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.54,0:21:00.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}恐怕會發怒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.35,0:21:03.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}會訓斥她  不可以如此輕賤別人的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:07.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}大人必須給孩子做個模範才行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.97,0:21:09.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.11,0:21:14.26,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柴拾來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.76,0:21:16.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這些夠了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.76,0:21:17.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.05,0:21:20.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我不是說過小心點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:22.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.57,0:21:24.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}只是沒看到路而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.37,0:21:42.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.12,0:21:45.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.63,0:21:51.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.61,0:21:53.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.68,0:21:58.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我有事想拜託柳也
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.58,0:22:04.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}雖然還多少有些難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.98,0:22:06.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你能看一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.12,0:23:48.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.71,0:23:54.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我沒見過自己的父母
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.98,0:23:57.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.80,0:24:00.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}大概  是被扔掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.17,0:24:05.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在路邊哭泣的時候  被行腳僧撿到了
